{"tid":2328730,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【科興】巴西指中國在緊急授權使用新冠疫苗方面不透明","createTime":"2020-12-16T17:16:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-16T17:21:50.000Z","uid":261647,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8daa8495dbda187df8450fcb522683da433e461f","tid":2328730,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T17:16:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1565440-20201215.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1565440-20201215.htm&d=c%2B6PkbrQ5MzYtHY5m9tE1wOzzNjRw9ZJ5YgnvwIkb18%3D&h=2aadfe95\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1565440-20201215.htm&h=b95abc56\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1565440-20201215.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n巴西衛生監管部門表示，中國在緊急授權使用新型冠狀病毒疫苗方面，並不透明。<br />\n<br />\n當局發表聲明，指巴西是評估中國科興疫苗的國際領導者，自6月以來，疫苗在中國獲得緊急使用授權，但中國的核准標準並不透明，亦無法取得有關中國決策標準的信息。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/FrontlineTechWorkersConcernGroup/posts/3796280090411696\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FFrontlineTechWorkersConcernGroup%2Fposts%2F3796280090411696&d=c%2B6PkbrQ5MzYtHY5m9tE1wOzzNjRw9ZJ5YgnvwIkb18%3D&h=bf690989\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/FrontlineTechWorkersConcernGroup/posts/3796280090411696</a><br />\n<br />\n作者：前線科技人員<br />\n<br />\n科興 Sinovac，即係香港政府買咗嗰隻。巴西政府唔識貨唔緊要，有我哋接貨 <img src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/t6c/1/16/1f4aa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fimages%2Femoji.php%2Fv9%2Ft6c%2F1%2F16%2F1f4aa.png&h=0765cdcc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"abc03a2987ba2e0ada29e5243fe96b7d7a808324","tid":2328730,"uid":227271,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T17:20:32.000Z","msg":"好不透明咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我就話係宇宙最透明<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n沒有，沒有，沒有，沒有，沒有，通過！"},{"pid":"e2aab7a76817b9f3da4c9ce7389bc02134ee57d0","tid":2328730,"uid":211003,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T17:21:50.000Z","msg":"傻嘅先買<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}